    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>PLAYTEST Available Q1 - 2026</u></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>It's Not Chess. It's Better! </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">PLUG &amp; PLAY. Nothing new to learn...just fun new moves &amp; easier gameplay.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Modes of play:</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Online Multiplayer  - Single Device Multiplayer - Battle the A.I. - Variant Options - Roguelike / Deckbuilder.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273750/extras/f5bbf1b89af11bc1ece81eb36f995e2d.poster.avif?t=1770780044\" width=1170 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273750/extras/f5bbf1b89af11bc1ece81eb36f995e2d.webm?t=1770780044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273750/extras/f5bbf1b89af11bc1ece81eb36f995e2d.mp4?t=1770780044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong> NEW Strategies. MORE Possibilities.</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Combine Powers</strong></u>: Move two pieces onto the same square using traditional chess moves to create powerful hybrids such as the &quot;BIOOK&quot;, Bishop + Rook, and move as either of the combined pieces.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Split Anytime:</strong></u> Either piece of a joined piece can move away as an individual piece in it’s traditional movement.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Risk &amp; Reward:</strong></u> Watch out! If your new hybrid piece, like a Queen + Knight, &quot;QUIGHT&quot;, gets taken you'll lose both your pieces.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273750/extras/2979ec68722a8061a83af4117fad1136.poster.avif?t=1770780044\" width=1170 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273750/extras/2979ec68722a8061a83af4117fad1136.webm?t=1770780044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273750/extras/2979ec68722a8061a83af4117fad1136.mp4?t=1770780044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>FASTER Promotions, MORE Often.</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Build your forces:</u> </strong>Get more queens with quick promotions. Combine the Rook with a Pawn then fast track it across the board for an extra queen.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Stage huge comebacks:</u></strong> Utilising quick promotions to tip the balance of power back in your favour.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Balanced at its core:</u></strong> Chessplus removes reliance on memorised plays. You must rely on sheer creativity to try and checkmate your opponent with adaptive, improvised gameplay.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273750/extras/ebc7db07820a8eed262665e5f5cba76a.poster.avif?t=1770780044\" width=780 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273750/extras/ebc7db07820a8eed262665e5f5cba76a.webm?t=1770780044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273750/extras/ebc7db07820a8eed262665e5f5cba76a.mp4?t=1770780044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>ROGUELIKE - Deckbuilder </strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Master Variants:</strong></u><strong> </strong>Battle progressively harder AI in different variants such as Fog of War and King of the Hill before taking on a Grandmaster boss battle. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Choices Matter:</u></strong> Every run is different. Every piece you sacrifice, card you add to your deck or mini-game you win will dramatically change the outcome of your run.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Battle your friends:</strong></u> Play against your friends in custom variants such as King of the Hill with the Roguelike ability cards enabled for drafting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
